<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,
  initial-scale=1.0">
  <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/static/stylesheets/style.css">
  <title>🤜🏻🤛🏻 Friends-pronos</title>
</head>

<body>



  <h1>Friends pronos</h1>
  <div class="welcome">
    <p>Welcome to this little soccer tournament game.</br>You have a group of friends and want to know
      who is the best bookmaker ?</br>Or you just want to face each other ?</br>
      This is your place.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="rules">
    <h2>The rules</h2>
    <p>Maximum of 5 players per competition.</br> Each week you will have 5 games selected by our team:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Find the winner = 1 point</li>
      <li>Find the right score = 3 points</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="starting">
    <p>Ready to start ?</br>Create your own competition</p>
    <input class="compName" type="text" placeholder="name of the competition">
    <a class="submitBtn" href="http://localhost:3000/playground">
      <button class="createComp">submit</button>
    </a>
  </div>


  <img class="pic1" src="static/images/bet.png" alt="fun fun fun">

  <script src="static/scripts/index.js"></script>
</body>

</html>